# 🇪🇸 Day 6 – Spanish Learning Journey

## 📌 Overview
Today focused on beginning Pimsleur Lesson 23, introducing new vocabulary and sentence structures. Due to the difficulty and volume of content, this lesson will likely require multiple days to fully memorize.

Additional vocabulary and phrases were practiced through Duolingo, Memrise, and Mango, with continued emphasis on real-world application.

---

## 🔵 Pimsleur (Primary Focus)
- Started Lesson 23
- Focused on:
- Flashcards
- Key vocabulary
- Initial exposure to new sentence structures

### Key Concepts:
- Se nos pinchó una llanta = We had a flat tire
- Pude = I could / I was able to
- En vez de = Instead of
- Hay una = There is one
- No sé lo que habría hecho = I don’t know what I would have done

### Notes:
Lesson 23 contains a large amount of new material and will require 2–3 days of repetition before progressing.

